{"tid":1510722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"緊急法真正用意-（永續議席）","createTime":"2019-08-27T09:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T04:23:11.000Z","uid":50457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"9cbf29422c0695aaa86d3a9b28c0736c01d4e14e","tid":1510722,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:44:46.000Z","msg":"借頭借路取消今年區議會，下年立法會選舉<br />\n<br />\n睇返最近民調就知，親中派係嚟緊兩大選舉會大敗，其實同時會折射出下一屆特首選委分配<br />\n<br />\n如果區議會連同立法會非親中派攞多200席，咁下一屆特首選舉，中共只有剛過600席，如果情況再差，隨時中共連半數控制權都無<br />\n<br />\n你諗下，如果出現呢個場面，中共會點？<br />\n<br />\n所以，唔排除緊急法的用意，係永續兩會議席<br />\n<br />\n點解民建聯等親中派咁想777推緊急法，就係想永續議席<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望估唔中，但以現在777政府已無視一切法律，已經不能排除呢個可能性"},{"pid":"c7da2b698f4a047ba0af487b06c54740a3bc65d5","tid":1510722,"uid":52817,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NSAWdB2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNSAWdB2.jpg&h=7e1fa5a5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"21d5b3551ea0cbb915077dc873d33a4c7f7307ab","tid":1510722,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:45:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PWzcvgg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPWzcvgg.jpg&h=187c67d0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=ec4db2c7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=854de76