,"tid":1510722,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c6c759ea355e46c5a2b0cf96b661a30f174ef94","tid":1510722,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"股票跌果陣夾硬停市，到開市跌得仲勁<br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔好咁大聲呀 到時藍絲都要走上街嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6744a97d685098ad33d914bbe54339b8e5fe5fe","tid":1510722,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6bd3e8d92393bb6d5e7608e7e5a59311d874b24c","tid":1510722,"uid":274658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c6c759ea355e46c5a2b0cf96b661a30f174ef94","tid":1510722,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:46:12.000Z","msg":"股票跌果陣夾硬停市，到開市跌得仲勁<br />\n好似係"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:53:56.000Z","msg":"唔好咁大聲呀 到時藍絲都要走上街嫁喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T09:54:14.000Z","msg":"殊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15566672565bb02806a87fd599165371ea6e26e","tid":1510722,"uid":111007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-27T10:47:52.000Z","msg":"唔好俾咁多豬知道呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f959572a44294d77842327aba2416a8e0f4c4a78","tid":1510722,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:52:56.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】風波未平　謝偉俊建議延後11月區議會選舉<br />\n<br />\n反對《逃犯條例》修訂引發連場衝突，至今仍未平息，區議會選舉將於11月舉行，選舉活動差不多要展開。不過社會紛爭未平息，或會影響各政團的助選活動。立法會議員謝偉俊今日（30日）在報章撰文，建議延後區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊在《am730》撰文，題為《緊急條例》，表示社會流傳港府正審慎考慮引用近百年前訂下的《緊急情況規例條例》，讓特首林鄭月娥認為屬於「緊急情況」及「危害公安」之下，制訂各種各乎公眾利益的規定。<br />\n<br />\n「緊急情況規例條例」未經司法覆核挑戰<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊表示，何謂「緊急情況」、「危害公安」，是因特首個人決定，因此屬於相對主觀觀念。而該項條例在《基本法》實施前制訂，在六七暴動後、回歸後一直備而未用，因此未經任何司法覆核挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n他又認為，由於是在非常時期的非常情況使用，「恐怕即使按該條例制定規例當中，部分可能被視為與一般（太平盛世下）受基本法保障人權有所抵觸，也未必會被法院随便推翻。」<br />\n<br />\n指助選活動或引發互相攻擊以至暴力事件<br />\n<br />\n謝偉俊提到，較多人談論立例禁止戴面罩參加遊行、示威活動，利用互聯網羣組發布虛假訊息及教唆各種違法行為等，他建議政府檢討是否應延後即將舉行的區議會選舉。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，一日騷亂未平，恐怕選舉會因各種不同陣營的助選活動，引發無休止的互相攻擊以至暴力事件，選民也難以平心靜氣地作出明智選擇。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.hk01.com/%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585/369799/%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E5%25BE%258C11%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589&amp;ved=0ahUKEwib3NzsqKrkAhWB62EKHQBtCjUQqQIIKCgBMAA&amp;usg=AOvVaw2J6uNVw4itUf-6-fSOZ-dj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Furl%3Fsa%3Dt%26source%3Dweb%26rct%3Dj%26url%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%2525E6%252594%2525BF%2525E6%252583%252585%2F369799%2F%2525E9%252580%252583%2525E7%25258A%2525AF%2525E6%2525A2%25259D%2525E4%2525BE%25258B-%2525E9%2525A2%2525A8%2525E6%2525B3%2525A2%2525E6%25259C%2525AA%2525E5%2525B9%2525B3-%2525E8%2525AC%25259D%2525E5%252581%252589%2525E4%2525BF%25258A%2525E5%2525BB%2525BA%2525E8%2525AD%2525B0%2525E5%2525BB%2525B6%2525E5%2525BE%25258C11%2525E6%25259C%252588%2525E5%25258D%252580%2525E8%2525AD%2525B0%2525E6%25259C%252583%2525E9%252581%2525B8%2525E8%252588%252589%26ved%3D0ahUKEwib3NzsqKrkAhWB62EKHQBtCjUQqQIIKCgBMAA%26usg%3DAOvVaw2J6uNVw4itUf-6-fSOZ-dj&d=9rGlslGXeLGLpJWMZA8bi6jD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=23a3cbaa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/url?sa=t&amp;source=web&amp;rct=j&amp;url=https://www.hk01.com/%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585/369799/%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2%25E6%259C%25AA%25E5%25B9%25B3-%25E8%25AC%259D%25E5%2581%2589%25E4%25BF%258A%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E5%25BB%25B6%25E5%25BE%258C11%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589&amp;ved=0ahUKEwib3NzsqKrkAhWB62EKHQBtCjUQqQIIKCgBMAA&amp;usg=AOvVaw2J6uNVw4itUf-6-fSOZ-dj</a>"},{"pid":"f140df799f4bac81ad2394f3aa9789b4dbb80014","tid":1510722,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-30T09:54:05.000Z","msg":"因為唔想港獨派透過區議會全取六席立法會議席"},{"pid":"63c1f9cb99dd08bf8184a731812c487ca0c694b3","tid":1510722,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T04:23:11.000Z","msg":"一個月前的推測愈來愈接近現實"}]}